---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - CALENDHUB"
  description="Privacy Policy for CALENDHUB AI-powered visual creation platform. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-text mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p class="text-text-muted text-lg mb-8">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-text">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              CALENDHUB ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our AI-powered visual creation platform.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold mb-3">2.1 Personal Information</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">We collect information you provide directly to us:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Account registration data (name, email address, username)</li>
              <li>Profile information and preferences</li>
              <li>Communication data (support tickets, feedback, surveys)</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mb-4">We do not store payment information - all payment processing is handled securely by third-party providers.</p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold mb-3">2.2 Content Data</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">We process content you upload or generate:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Images and videos you upload for processing</li>
              <li>Text prompts and generation parameters</li>
              <li>Generated content and editing history</li>
              <li>Custom training data for LoRa models</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold mb-3">2.3 Technical Information</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">We automatically collect technical data only with your consent (via cookie acceptance):</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Device information (browser type, operating system)</li>
              <li>Usage analytics (features used, session duration)</li>
              <li>Analytics cookies for website performance tracking</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mb-4">We do not store IP addresses or geolocation data.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">We use your information to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Provide and improve our AI generation services</li>
              <li>Manage your account and subscription</li>
              <li>Communicate with you about service updates and support</li>
              <li>Ensure platform security and prevent fraud</li>
              <li>Analyze usage patterns to enhance user experience</li>
              <li>Comply with legal obligations and enforce our terms</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mb-4">We do not use your personal information or content to train our AI models.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">4. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties, except in these limited situations:</p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold mb-3">4.1 Legal Requirements</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">We may disclose information only when required by Albanian law or to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Comply with legal processes or court orders</li>
              <li>Protect our rights, property, or safety</li>
              <li>Prevent fraud or security threats</li>
              <li>Enforce our Terms of Service</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">5. Data Security</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">We implement robust security measures to protect your information:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>TLS 1.2 encryption for data transmission</li>
              <li>AES encryption for data storage</li>
              <li>Regular security audits and vulnerability assessments</li>
              <li>Access controls and authentication systems</li>
              <li>Daily backups across multiple AWS availability zones</li>
              <li>Employee training on data protection practices</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">6. Data Retention</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">We retain your information for different periods:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Account data: Until account deletion or 1 year of inactivity</li>
              <li>Generated content: As per your subscription plan or until deletion</li>
              <li>Usage analytics: Up to 12 months in aggregated form</li>
              <li>Payment records: 5 years as required by Albanian tax law</li>
              <li>Support communications: 1 year from last interaction</li>
              <li>All personal data is deleted within 1 month after account deletion</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">7. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">You have the following rights regarding your personal information:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request copies of your personal information</li>
              <li><strong>Rectification:</strong> Correct inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
              <li><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your personal information</li>
              <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a machine-readable format</li>
              <li><strong>Withdraw consent:</strong> Revoke consent for cookies and analytics</li>
              <li><strong>Account deletion:</strong> Delete your account and all associated data</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mb-4">To exercise these rights, contact us at contact@calendhub.com.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">8. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">We use cookies only for analytics tracking to understand website usage patterns. These cookies are only placed with your explicit consent through our cookie banner.</p>
            <p class="mb-4">You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings or our cookie banner at any time.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">9. International Data Transfers</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Your information may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your residence. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place, including Standard Contractual Clauses and adequacy decisions where applicable.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">10. Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Our Service is not directed to children under 13 (or 16 in the EU). We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we learn we have collected such information, we will delete it promptly.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">11. Third-Party Links</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              While our Service generally does not contain links to third-party websites, if any such links are present, we are not responsible for their privacy practices. We encourage you to read their privacy policies before providing any information.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">12. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of material changes via email or through our Service. The "Last Updated" date reflects the most recent changes.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">13. Contact Information</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              For privacy-related questions, concerns, or requests, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-border/30 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <p class="mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> contact@calendhub.com</p>
              <p class="mb-2"><strong>Location:</strong> Albania</p>
              <p><strong>Response Time:</strong> We respond to privacy requests within 30 days</p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>